extensions.description: By the Creator of ABSOLUTE CINEMA MEME

Hypernode is a distributed intelligence network that transforms idle computing power into an autonomous, incentivized ecosystem of AI agents and sub-networks. Each node acts as both observer and contributor, running telemetry, computation, and coordination processes that feed a collective neural fabric. Designed to evolve through data, performance, and self-optimization, Hypernode aims to become the intelligent infrastructure layer of the decentralized internet
